Gates Apologizes for U.S. Helicopter Strikes That Killed Nine Afghan Boys

-- B y   E l t a f   N a j a f i z a d a
-- 
2011-03-07T15:10:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-07/gates-apologizes-for-u-s-helicopter-strikes-that-killed-nine-afghan-boys.html
Defense Secretary  Robert Gates 
apologized for U.S. helicopter strikes in  Afghanistan  that
killed nine boys cutting firewood on a forested mountainside
after they were mistaken for Taliban. Gates made his comments
today in Kabul at a press conference.  To contact the reporter on this story:
